cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.SD, cs.CY

This paper deals with the detection and summarization of real-world events using Twitter and news data. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also involves natural language processing and text summarization techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper involves data analysis and machine learning techniques, which could place it in cs.SD (Software Engineering) or cs.CY (Computers and Society).
